trans-unit.source: Provides a listener that routes all tracing and debugging output to the IIS 7.0 infrastructure.
The <xref:System.Web.IisTraceListener> class connects the tracing mechanism of [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] to [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)].

This listener class enables developers who create [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] applications and who implement the <xref:System.Web.IHttpModule> and <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler> interfaces to raise page-level, module-level, or handler-level events to the [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] infrastructure when tracing is enabled.
This listener class does not route [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] events to ASP.NET classes.
This includes the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> class and classes that implement the <xref:System.Web.IHttpModule> or <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler> interface.
<xref:System.Web.IisTraceListener> is introduced in the [!INCLUDE[net_v35_long](~/includes/net-v35-long-md.md)].
For more information, see [Versions and Dependencies](~/docs/framework/migration-guide/versions-and-dependencies.md).
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.IisTraceListener"></xref> class.
<xref:System.Web.IisTraceListener.%23ctor%2A> is introduced in the [!INCLUDE[net_v35_long](~/includes/net-v35-long-md.md)].
For more information, see [Versions and Dependencies](~/docs/framework/migration-guide/versions-and-dependencies.md).
Writes trace information, a data object, and event information to the output of the <xref href="System.Web.IisTraceListener"></xref> class.
This method is not intended to be called directly by application code.

The members of the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Debug?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace?displayProperty=fullName>, and <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource?displayProperty=fullName> classes use this method to write trace data.
<xref:System.Web.IisTraceListener.TraceData%2A> is introduced in the [!INCLUDE[net_v35_long](~/includes/net-v35-long-md.md)].
For more information, see [Versions and Dependencies](~/docs/framework/migration-guide/versions-and-dependencies.md).
A <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceEventCache"></xref> object that contains the current process ID, thread ID, and stack trace information.
A name that identifies the output.
This is typically the name of the application that generated the trace event.
A <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceEventType"></xref> value that specifies the type of event that caused the trace.
A numeric identifier for the event.
The trace data to write.

For more information, see [Versions and Dependencies](~/docs/framework/migration-guide/versions-and-dependencies.md).
